= Publications 
[https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/author/37088952001 \[IEEE Xplore\]][https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=nYQ18kQAAAAJ&hl=en \[Google Scholar\]][https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Anuj-Yadav-12 \[Research Gate\]][https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7763-3787 \[ORCID\]]\n

This page includes the list of my research publications, some of which are published, under review and under preparation. Please feel free to contact me or my co-authors for the extended versions of the published work or preprints of the work yet to be published.\n

*Remark:* Publications marked with asterisk *(\*)* follow aphabetical author order.

